headline: Canada Goose Holdings Stock Sees RS Rating Fly Higher
summary: When putting together your watch list, look for stocks with an 80 or higher RS Rating. Canada Goose Holdings stock is one stock that just reached the mark, now earning a score of 86.    Hone Your Stock-Picking Skills By Focusing On These Factors  IBD's unique RS Rating identifies technical performance by using a 1 (worst) to 99 (best) score that identifies how a stock's price action over the trailing 52 weeks matches up against the rest of the market.
